#Lyrics
Save Your people, O Lord, and bless Your heritage. Govern and uphold them now and always. Day by day we bless You. We praise Your name forever. Lord, keep us this night without sin. Have mercy on us, O Lord, have mercy on us. Show us Your mercy, O Lord. And grant us Your salvation. O Lord, hear our prayer. And let our cry come to You.

